<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada orang yang keluar
lewat gerbang selatan.</font>

4
00:00:23,850 --> 00:00:25,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa kudaku./ Ya.</font>

5
00:00:38,570 --> 00:00:39,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang itu.</font>

6
00:01:04,390 --> 00:01:05,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan tandunya!</font>

7
00:01:08,970 --> 00:01:10,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang didalam?</font>

8
00:01:13,940 --> 00:01:15,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang ini tidak...</font>

9
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:18,710
<font color=#FFFF00>...melihat kebelakang sama sekali
meskipun orang-orang...</font>

10
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:20,380
<font color=#FFFF00>...teriak dan lari.</font>

11
00:02:08,090 --> 00:02:09,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Biarkan kami pergi.</font>

12
00:02:09,630 --> 00:02:10,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia terluka.</font>

13
00:02:14,460 --> 00:02:16,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Beraninya kau menyentuhnya?</font>

14
00:02:16,970 --> 00:02:18,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Lebih baik kalian
membiarkan kami pergi.</font>

15
00:02:18,900 --> 00:02:20,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Singkirkan pedangmu dari So Ah,</font>

16
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:22,710
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan keluar.</font>

17
00:02:23,270 --> 00:02:24,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang!</font>

18
00:02:24,270 --> 00:02:27,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika ini menjadi masalah yang lebih besar,
maka posisimu akan bahaya.</font>

19
00:02:29,450 --> 00:02:30,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak apa-apa jika begitu?</font>

20
00:02:33,350 --> 00:02:34,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau.../ Jeoha.</font>

21
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:38,550
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ini perintah Raja.</i></font>

22
00:02:39,620 --> 00:02:41,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya sudah terlambat.</font>

23
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja Jeoha.</font>

24
00:02:52,970 --> 00:02:55,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda harus mundur.
Ini perintah Raja.</font>

25
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:58,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka semua mendapat
perintah dari Raja.</font>

26
00:03:06,220 --> 00:03:08,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhenti. Hentikan.</font>

27
00:03:10,750 --> 00:03:13,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah bersamanya?</font>

28
00:03:13,820 --> 00:03:15,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

29
00:03:18,530 --> 00:03:20,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah mendapatkannya.</font>

30
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:28,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kalian lakukan?
Bawa mereka.</font>

31
00:03:33,340 --> 00:03:35,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepas. Lepaskan!</font>

32
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:43,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Beraninya kau melarangku?</font>

33
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:45,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika anda tidak mematuhi perintah Raja,</font>

34
00:03:45,690 --> 00:03:48,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana anda akan
menangani akibatnya nanti?</font>

35
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:50,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda harus kembali ke istana.</font>

36
00:03:50,390 --> 00:03:52,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan memberitahu Raja...</font>

37
00:03:55,730 --> 00:03:58,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian... kalian...</font>

38
00:03:58,630 --> 00:04:00,900
<font color=#FFFF00>...seharusnya tidak membuatku
marah.</font>

39
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:03,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengan begitu, aku
tidak akan melawanmu,</font>

40
00:04:04,140 --> 00:04:05,580
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia, dan Apamama.</font>

41
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:07,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu artinya...</font>

42
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:10,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan menyesali ini.</font>

43
00:04:22,330 --> 00:04:23,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Raja.</font>

44
00:04:25,460 --> 00:04:27,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang harus kita lakukan?</font>

45
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:31,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia ini memang selalu bersikap
berlebihan.</font>

46
00:04:31,570 --> 00:04:34,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja Jeoha.../
Aku tidak akan menemuinya.</font>

47
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:38,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa kali aku harus memberi tahumu?
Aku menyuruhnya diam di kamar.</font>

48
00:04:38,710 --> 00:04:42,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku rasa dia sudah kehilangan akalnya.</font>

49
00:04:44,250 --> 00:04:46,550
<font color=#FFFF00>So Ah! So Ah!</font>

50
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:49,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana kau, So Ah?</font>

51
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:52,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana kau, So Ah?
Jawab aku!</font>

52
00:04:53,660 --> 00:04:54,960
<font color=#FFFF00>So Ah!</font>

53
00:04:57,060 --> 00:04:58,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang sedang kalian lakukan?</font>

54
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:01,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir!/ Seja Jeoha.</font>

55
00:05:06,970 --> 00:05:09,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Raja memerintahkanku
untuk membawamu menemuinya.</font>

56
00:05:25,290 --> 00:05:29,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti sudah kehilangan akal,
beraninya menghancurkan istanaku.</font>

57
00:05:29,930 --> 00:05:32,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang gila telah menculik
salah satu rakyatku.</font>

58
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku dengar dia lari kesini.</font>

59
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:37,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau tidak mematuhi
perintah kurunganku?</font>

60
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus menemukannya.
Tolong izinkan aku.</font>

61
00:05:39,340 --> 00:05:40,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bukanlah orang
yang harus kau cari.</font>

62
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:42,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia adalah buktiku.</font>

63
00:05:44,610 --> 00:05:46,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda sudah tahu tentang ini?</font>

64
00:05:46,140 --> 00:05:51,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir aku tidak tahu apa yang
kau lakukan di belakangku?</font>

65
00:05:54,980 --> 00:05:58,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak tahu perkataan
apa yang dikatakan manusia licik itu, tapi...</font>

66
00:05:58,390 --> 00:06:00,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada yang lebih buruk
dari pengkhianatanmu.</font>

67
00:06:02,290 --> 00:06:05,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa sulit bagimu
untuk menunggu?</font>

68
00:06:05,930 --> 00:06:09,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau tidak bisa
menunggu sampai aku mati?</font>

69
00:06:09,330 --> 00:06:11,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang sudah
anda dengar?</font>

70
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:13,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Tutup mulutmu.
Aku tidak ingin mendengar apapun.</font>

71
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:20,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini semua karena kau.</font>

72
00:06:20,980 --> 00:06:24,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ikut campur hubungan
Ayah dan anak.</font>

73
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:25,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihat.</font>

74
00:06:25,780 --> 00:06:29,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja Jeoha, yang sangat
baik hati, sekarang berani melawan.</font>

75
00:06:33,620 --> 00:06:36,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau akan keluar
dan memperburuk keadaan?</font>

76
00:06:37,290 --> 00:06:39,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Apamama./
Tutup mulutmu!</font>

77
00:06:47,470 --> 00:06:48,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau...</font>

78
00:06:49,970 --> 00:06:53,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Akulah Raja yang membawa
perdamaian di Goryeo...</font>

79
00:06:53,410 --> 00:06:56,380
<font color=#FFFF00>...setelah 100
tahun kehancurannya.</font>

80
00:06:59,020 --> 00:07:01,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika bukan karena aku,
negara ini pasti...</font>

81
00:07:01,180 --> 00:07:04,820
<font color=#FFFF00>...sudah lenyap seperti negara-negara
lain di perbatasan.</font>

82
00:07:05,890 --> 00:07:08,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu bagaimana
cara aku melindungi Goryeo?</font>

83
00:07:08,460 --> 00:07:12,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengemis kepada Kaisar
meski dihina.</font>

84
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:15,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengemis padanya
selama lima tahun.</font>

85
00:07:15,330 --> 00:07:16,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika anda bicara
tentang Omamama...</font>

86
00:07:16,870 --> 00:07:20,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, begitulah cara
aku menikahi Ibumu,</font>

87
00:07:20,570 --> 00:07:22,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Putri Kaisar!</font>

88
00:07:22,670 --> 00:07:23,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan.</font>

89
00:07:23,670 --> 00:07:25,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku rasa ini belum cukup,
itu sebabnya aku memilikimu.</font>

90
00:07:25,810 --> 00:07:28,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan./
Aku lahir untuk Goryeo.</font>

91
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong hentikan!</font>

92
00:07:29,810 --> 00:07:33,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan sampai sekarang, istriku
bertindak kejam padaku,</font>

93
00:07:33,020 --> 00:07:35,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Anaknya selalu mengincar
posisiku,</font>

94
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:38,860
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan dia bahkan datang dalam
mimpi untuk mencekikku.</font>

95
00:07:51,630 --> 00:07:53,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda menghina Ibuku...</font>

96
00:07:54,270 --> 00:07:56,210
<font color=#FFFF00>...di hadapan dia?</font>

97
00:07:56,210 --> 00:07:57,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Rakyatku mengatakan...</font>

98
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,710
<font color=#FFFF00>...bahwa mereka
sangat mengkhawatirkanku.</font>

99
00:08:01,580 --> 00:08:02,780
<font color=#FFFF00>"Sebentar lagi..."</font>

100
00:08:02,780 --> 00:08:06,080
<font color=#FFFF00>"Anjing kampung akan
memerintah negara ini."</font>

101
00:08:06,180 --> 00:08:08,620
<font color=#FFFF00>"Dia sudah memiliki 2 dari
3 yang dia butuhkan."</font>

102
00:08:10,150 --> 00:08:11,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha.</font>

103
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:15,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda harus tenang.</font>

104
00:08:18,490 --> 00:08:21,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau ingin Goryeo diberikan kepada
orang seperti dia?</font>

105
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:23,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka mengambil tanah rakyat,</font>

106
00:08:23,270 --> 00:08:24,900
<font color=#FFFF00>...memperbudak putra mereka,</font>

107
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:27,370
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan melakukan kekerasan pada
putri mereka.</font>

108
00:08:33,310 --> 00:08:34,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa...</font>

109
00:08:35,780 --> 00:08:36,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa...</font>

110
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:39,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang bisa
anda lakukan selain...</font>

111
00:08:39,850 --> 00:08:41,580
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidur dan pergi berburu?</font>

112
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:42,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau...</font>

113
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:45,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pasti sudah gila,
dan ingin membunuhku.</font>

114
00:08:48,090 --> 00:08:50,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika anda takut, anda
seharusnya sudah puas...</font>

115
00:08:51,930 --> 00:08:54,530
<font color=#FFFF00>...ketika aku terus menunduk
seperti anak bodoh padamu.</font>

116
00:08:58,130 --> 00:08:59,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Lancang.</font>

117
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:01,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda seharusnya
tidak melakukan apapun...</font>

118
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:05,610
<font color=#FFFF00>...supaya tidak membuat aku atau kakekku,
Kaisar Yuan marah.</font>

119
00:09:05,610 --> 00:09:07,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau sekarang...</font>

120
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:09,950
<font color=#FFFF00>...menunjukkan sifat aslimu?</font>

121
00:09:10,950 --> 00:09:11,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

122
00:09:30,670 --> 00:09:32,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia masih didalam.</font>

123
00:09:32,170 --> 00:09:34,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Pengawal kita sudah
berjaga disetiap tempat.</font>

124
00:09:35,510 --> 00:09:37,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka
akan bergerak malam ini.</font>

125
00:09:37,870 --> 00:09:39,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan berjaga-jaga.</font>

126
00:09:44,580 --> 00:09:45,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

127
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:48,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa membawa
penjaga Ratu.</font>

128
00:09:49,090 --> 00:09:50,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha.../
Hentikan.</font>

129
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:51,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kau bicarakan...</font>

130
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:54,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu apa yang
akan kau katakan.</font>

131
00:09:54,860 --> 00:09:55,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan.</font>

132
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:58,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergilah dan bawa So Ah.</font>

133
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi?</font>

134
00:10:09,570 --> 00:10:11,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku lebih peduli dengan...</font>

135
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:14,480
<font color=#FFFF00>...apa yang akan terjadi nanti.</font>

136
00:10:21,750 --> 00:10:23,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia putri
Menteri Keuangan?</font>

137
00:10:24,050 --> 00:10:25,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Raja.</font>

138
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:29,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Wanita yang hampir
menikahi Wang Jeon?</font>

139
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:32,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah kau wanita
yang pernah aku undang?</font>

140
00:10:32,530 --> 00:10:34,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau memakai cadar.</font>

141
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:37,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Itu dia.</font>

142
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:38,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi...</font>

143
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:41,770
<font color=#FFFF00>...Seja menginginkan
harta Tuan Eun,</font>

144
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:43,470
<font color=#FFFF00>...sehingga dia menghentikan
pernikahannya,</font>

145
00:10:43,470 --> 00:10:45,840
<font color=#FFFF00>...menculiknya, dan mencoba
menyakitinya?</font>

146
00:10:46,010 --> 00:10:47,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar.</font>

147
00:10:47,610 --> 00:10:49,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah mengapa...</font>

148
00:10:49,450 --> 00:10:51,210
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku menyelamatkannya.</font>

149
00:10:51,310 --> 00:10:54,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia terluka dalam pertarungan itu.</font>

150
00:10:54,580 --> 00:10:56,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Raja, itu...</font>

151
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:57,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak apa-apa, Nona.</font>

152
00:10:57,820 --> 00:11:00,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami akan melindungimu
mulai sekarang.</font>

153
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:04,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak percaya binatang
itu ternyata Seja.</font>

154
00:11:04,430 --> 00:11:06,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka berbohong
padamu, Raja.</font>

155
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:09,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja Jeoha bukanlah
orang seperti itu.</font>

156
00:11:10,330 --> 00:11:11,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia adalah Rajamu.</font>

157
00:11:11,730 --> 00:11:13,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau hanya boleh bicara
jika diizinkan.</font>

158
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:17,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekretaris Asisten Kerajaan./ Ya, Raja.</font>

159
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:19,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan
menurunkan tahta Seja.</font>

160
00:11:20,610 --> 00:11:24,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Buat perintah tertulis
di <i>perkamen</i>.</font>

161
00:11:20,610 --> 00:11:24,210
<font color=#FFFF00>{\an8}*media untuk menulis yang dibuat dari kulit binatang.</font>

162
00:11:24,210 --> 00:11:26,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan melaksanakan
perintah anda.</font>

163
00:11:29,690 --> 00:11:31,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Raja. Raja.</font>

164
00:11:33,190 --> 00:11:36,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa anda malah mempercayai mereka
bukannya anak anda?</font>

165
00:11:36,890 --> 00:11:39,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah macam apa
yang akan melakukan itu?</font>

166
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:43,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Merekalah orang yang menculikku.</font>

167
00:11:43,570 --> 00:11:46,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka berbohong untuk
menjebak Seja Jeoha.</font>

168
00:11:46,470 --> 00:11:48,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa anda tidak sadar?</font>

169
00:11:48,740 --> 00:11:52,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika ada yang mengatakan Seja
tidak boleh diturunkan,</font>

170
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,910
<font color=#FFFF00>...buat dia untuk
melihat buktinya.</font>

171
00:11:57,450 --> 00:11:59,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Jelaskan bagaimana Seja
mencoba menyakitinya...</font>

172
00:12:00,450 --> 00:12:02,690
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk mendapatkan
harta Ayahnya.</font>

173
00:12:02,690 --> 00:12:03,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, Raja.</font>

174
00:12:03,890 --> 00:12:06,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan melaksanakan
perintah anda.</font>

175
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan juga,</font>

176
00:12:07,620 --> 00:12:09,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika dia terus
berbicara omong kosong,</font>

177
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:11,460
<font color=#FFFF00>...potong lidahnya.</font>

178
00:12:12,930 --> 00:12:16,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang-orang akan mengira itu
tindakan Seja.</font>

179
00:12:32,350 --> 00:12:35,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Utusan sudah menunggu anda
di jamuan makan.</font>

180
00:12:44,190 --> 00:12:45,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini jebakan.</font>

181
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Jebakan?</font>

182
