00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:14,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku terkena saat ingin melarikan diri.</font>

363
00:27:15,530 --> 00:27:19,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku seharusnya menangkisnya.
Sepertinya aku harus berlatih lebih keras.</font>

364
00:27:22,770 --> 00:27:23,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Orabeoni.</font>

365
00:27:24,870 --> 00:27:25,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya?</font>

366
00:27:26,180 --> 00:27:27,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Ambil ini.</font>

367
00:27:28,480 --> 00:27:31,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Bersihkan darahnya.
Aku harus mengambil lebih banyak obat.</font>

368
00:27:31,950 --> 00:27:33,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan, ini...</font>

369
00:27:34,580 --> 00:27:36,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sangat ahli dalam hal ini.</font>

370
00:27:36,450 --> 00:27:39,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapanpun aku terluka atau
sakit, dia akan merawatku.</font>

371
00:27:55,300 --> 00:27:57,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan padaku. Biar aku saja.</font>

372
00:28:35,140 --> 00:28:36,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Rambutmu...</font>

373
00:29:03,870 --> 00:29:06,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Biar aku saja
dan kau bisa pergi menemui Seja Jeoha.</font>

374
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:09,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka akan mengadakan
rapat dewan.</font>

375
00:29:09,450 --> 00:29:12,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka akan membuat
tuduhan palsu...</font>

376
00:29:12,120 --> 00:29:14,550
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menurunkannya.../
Diam.</font>

377
00:29:16,190 --> 00:29:17,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bergerak.</font>

378
00:29:21,720 --> 00:29:23,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pasti sudah memperkirakan itu.</font>

379
00:29:24,260 --> 00:29:25,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sudah tahu.</font>

380
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:29,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Terkadang, aku berharap dia
berhenti memikirkan itu.</font>

381
00:29:29,670 --> 00:29:31,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi sepertinya dia tidak
mampu.</font>

382
00:29:33,170 --> 00:29:34,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia terus berpikir...</font>

383
00:29:36,110 --> 00:29:37,710
<font color=#FFFF00>...setiap saat.</font>

